trans-unit.source: Represents a window that supports content navigation.
trans-unit.target: Representerar ett fönster som har stöd för innehåll navigering.

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow derives from <xref:System.Windows.Window> and extends it with the ability to navigate to and display content.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow härleds från <xref:System.Windows.Window>och utökar möjlighet att navigera till och visa innehåll.</xref:System.Windows.Window>

trans-unit.source: Content can be any [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] object or [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] file.
trans-unit.target: Innehållet kan vara någon [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winfx](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winfx-md.md)] objekt eller [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_html](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-html-md.md)] filen.

trans-unit.source: In general, however, a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page> object is the preferred way to package content for navigation.
trans-unit.target: I allmänhet, men en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>objektet är det bästa sättet att paketinnehåll för navigering.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Page>

trans-unit.source: Content can be navigated to by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> property with the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the desired content.
trans-unit.target: Innehåll som kan öppnas efter att genom att ange den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>egenskap med det [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för önskat innehåll.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, content can be navigated to by using one of the following overloads of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> When content is navigated to by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow will return an object that contains the content.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom innehåll kan öppnas efter att på något av följande överlagringar av den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metod:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29>när innehållet har navigerat till av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)], NavigationWindow returnerar ett objekt som innehåller innehållet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Navigation by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] also supports navigation to a content fragment.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Navigering av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] har också stöd för navigering till innehåll-fragment.

trans-unit.source: See <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, content can be navigated to by using one of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method overloads that accepts an object: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> The lifetime of a navigation can be tracked through the following events: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.
trans-unit.target: Alternativt innehåll kan navigerat till något av de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metoden överlagringar som accepterar ett objekt:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29>livslängden för navigering kan spåras via följande händelser:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted>- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.FragmentNavigation> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationStopped> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationFailed> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.NavigationProgress> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigating> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%2CSystem.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%28System.Object%29> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Not all events are raised each time that a navigation occurs; the set of events that are raised is determined by the type of navigation that occurs (content or content fragment) and how the navigation completes (canceled, stopped, or failed).
trans-unit.target: Inte alla händelser aktiveras varje gång en navigation inträffar; uppsättningen av händelser som är bestäms av typ av navigering som uppstår (innehåll eller innehåll fragment) och hur navigeringen har slutförts (avbrutits, stoppas eller misslyckades).

trans-unit.source: The following figure illustrates the sequence in which these events will fire: ![Page navigation flow chart](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "Page navigation flow chart") During or after a navigation, NavigationWindow provides information about the content that is being navigated to, including the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the content being navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the current content (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), and an object that contains the content that was navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Följande bild illustrerar sekvensen som händelserna ska utlösas: ![sidan navigering flödesschema](~/add/media/navigationoverviewfigure11.png "sidan navigering flödesschema") under eller efter en navigering NavigationWindow innehåller information om det innehåll som är att navigerat till, inklusive den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] av innehåll som har navigerat till (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>), [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] för det aktuella innehållet (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A>), och ett objekt som innehåller det innehåll som har navigerat till (<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl.Content%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CurrentSource%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: When content is navigated to, NavigationWindow records the navigation as an entry in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: När innehållet har navigerat till registrerar NavigationWindow navigering som en post i historik.

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to back navigation history when either a new navigation occurs, by calling the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A> method, or by navigating to an entry in forward navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En post har lagts till i tillbaka historik när en ny navigering inträffar genom att anropa den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>metoden, eller genom att gå till en post i historiken för navigering framåt, genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A>

trans-unit.source: An entry is added to forward navigation history by navigating to an entry in back navigation history, by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.
trans-unit.target: En post har lagts till i historiken för navigering framåt genom att gå till en post i tillbaka historik, genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A> report whether there are entries in back and forward navigation history, respectively.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A>rapportera om det finns poster i tillbaka och navigering framåt historik respektive.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoForward%2A></xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.CanGoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first time that one piece of content is navigated to from another piece of content, NavigationWindow automatically displays a navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that allows users to navigate back and forwards through navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Första gången som en del av innehåll navigerat till från en annan typ av innehåll, NavigationWindow visas automatiskt navigering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] som användarna kan gå tillbaka och vidarebefordrar via historik.

trans-unit.source: You can configure when the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is shown by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan konfigurera när navigeringen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] visas genom att ange den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ShowsNavigationUI%2A>

trans-unit.source: The most recent entry in back navigation history can be removed by calling <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Den senaste posten i tillbaka Historik kan tas bort genom att anropa <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow does not store an instance of a content object in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow lagrar inte en instans av ett innehållsobjekt i historik.

trans-unit.source: Instead, NavigationWindow creates a new instance of the content object each time it is navigated to by using navigation history.
trans-unit.target: I stället skapar NavigationWindow en ny instans av innehållsobjektet varje gång den navigeras till med hjälp av historik.

trans-unit.source: This behavior is designed to avoid excessive memory consumption when large numbers and large pieces of content are being navigated to.
trans-unit.target: Det här beteendet är utformat för att undvika överdriven minnesförbrukning när stora tal och stora delar av innehåll som du navigerar till.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the state of the content is not remembered from one navigation to the next.
trans-unit.target: Därför sparas inte tillståndet för innehållet från en navigering till nästa.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] provides several techniques by which you can store a piece of state for a piece of content in navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Dock [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] innehåller flera metoder som du kan lagra en typ av tillstånd för en del av innehåll i historik.

trans-unit.source: Using <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, you can also remember multiple sets of state for a single page instance.
trans-unit.target: Med hjälp av <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, du kan också komma ihåg flera uppsättningar av tillståndet för en enstaka sida-instans.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>

trans-unit.source: NavigationWindow is one of two navigators in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], the other being <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.
trans-unit.target: NavigationWindow är en av två tidsnavigatörer i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], den som <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: Essentially, navigator is a class supports navigation and navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Navigator är i princip en klass har stöd för navigering och historik.

trans-unit.source: Visually, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] use [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] as a navigator, to provide an integrated user experience.
trans-unit.target: Visuellt, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] använder [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] som en navigator att ge en integrerad användarupplevelse.

trans-unit.source: However, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] actually use NavigationWindow as the navigator; the <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A> property of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] running in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] will return a reference to the NavigationWindow, and the navigation history that is managed by the NavigationWindow is integrated with the navigation history that is managed by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Dock [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] faktiskt använder NavigationWindow som Navigatören; den <xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>egenskapen för ett [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] körs i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)] returnerar en referens till NavigationWindow och den historik som hanteras av NavigationWindow är integrerad med den historik som hanteras av [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.Application.MainWindow%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Content Model:** NavigationWindow is a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, which means that NavigationWindow can contain content such as text, images, or panels.
trans-unit.target: **Innehållsmodellen:** NavigationWindow är en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>, vilket innebär att NavigationWindow kan innehålla innehåll, t.ex text, bilder eller paneler.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ContentControl>

trans-unit.source: Also, NavigationWindow is a root element and, consequently, cannot be part of another element's content.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom NavigationWindow är ett rotelement och därför kan inte vara en del av en annan elementinnehåll.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the content model for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, see [WPF Content Model](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om innehållsmodellen för <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>, se [WPF innehåll modellen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Button>

trans-unit.source: Customizing the NavigationWindow Control To apply the same property settings to multiple NavigationWindow controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Anpassa den NavigationWindow kontroll att använda samma egenskapsinställningar för flera NavigationWindow kontroller, Använd den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can modify the default <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> to give the control a unique appearance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ändra standard <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>att ge unik för kontrollen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: For more information about creating a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, see [Customizing the Appearance of an Existing Control by Creating a ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Mer information om hur du skapar en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, se [anpassa utseendet på en befintlig kontroll genom att skapa en ControlTemplate](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>

trans-unit.source: To see the parts and states that are specific to the NavigationWindow, see [NavigationWindow Styles and Templates](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Delar och tillstånd som är specifika för NavigationWindow finns [NavigationWindow format och mallar](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.target: Om en egenskapen anges av ett standardformat kan egenskapen ändras från standardvärdet när kontrollen visas i programmet.

trans-unit.source: The default style is determined by which desktop theme is used when the application is running.
trans-unit.target: Standardformatet som bestäms av vilka tema används när programmet körs.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Default WPF Themes](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=158252).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether a <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref> isolates external [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] content within a partial trust security sandbox (with default Internet zone permission set).
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om en <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref> isolerar externa [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)] innehåll i ett partiellt förtroende säkerhet sandbox (med behörighetsgruppen standard Internet zon).

trans-unit.source: External content is [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] content that is not included with an application as either a resource file or a content file (for more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).
trans-unit.target: Externt innehåll är [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] innehåll som inte ingår i en resursfil eller en innehållsfil i ett program (Mer information finns i [resurs för WPF-program, innehåll och datafiler](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)).

trans-unit.source: When SandboxExternalContent is true, and the content of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> is an external [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] file, the content is loaded into a partial trust security sandbox that is limited to the default Internet zone permission set.
trans-unit.target: När SandboxExternalContent är true och innehållet i den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>är en extern [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] filen innehållet har lästs in i ett partiellt förtroende säkerhet sandbox som är begränsad till standardvärdet behörighetsgruppen Internet-zon.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the external content is loaded into a separate process.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom laddas externt innehåll i en separat process.

trans-unit.source: Consequently, the external content becomes isolated and does not have access to application-scope resources, such as resource dictionaries (for more information, see <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>).
trans-unit.target: Följaktligen externt innehåll blir isolerade och inte har åtkomst till program som definitionsområde resurser, till exempel resursordlistor (Mer information finns i <xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>).</xref:System.Windows.ResourceDictionary>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> contains external content only when the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> property is set to the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for an external [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] file.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>innehåller externa innehåll bara när den <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A>egenskap är inställd på den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] för en extern [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] fil.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>
